high_descs: Go forward and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the apple on the left.
Turn around and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, shut the door and then open it and pick up the apple and shut the door.
Turn to face the counter to the right.
Put the apple down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple on the counter.

high_descs: Move to the fridge in front and to the left of you.
Pick up a apple from the fridge and close the door.
Move to the microwave to the right of the fridge.
Place the apple inside and heat it before removing it and closing the door.
Turn to the right standing where you are.
Place the apple on the counter.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and remove the apple that is on the top shelf.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and begin walking forward, turn left again and walk up to the microwave.

Open the microwave door and place the apple inside then close the door, turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds turn off the microwave, open the door and remove the apple, then close the microwave door.
Turn right and walk up to the counter.
Place the heated apple on the counter in front and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on the counter.

high_descs: Walk forward and go to the fridge on your left.
Take an apple out of the fridge.
Go to the microwave on your right.
Heat the apple and then pick it up again.
Turn to your right to face the toaster.
Put the apple on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the counter to the left of the toaster.
